Labels: routing, milestone-1

âœï¸ MILESTONE 2: Book Creation & Tag System

Estimated: 3â€“4 days

M2.1: AddBookPanel Component

Description: Interface for adding a new book.
Checklist:

 Add title, author, genre, and description fields

